results.title: Astonishing X-Men (2004) #59
results.description: Back from their honeymoon, Northstar and Kyle face a threat at home……while Northstar faces another threat all on his own!And deep in space, something is coming that might literally tear the team apart!

results.title: Astonishing X-Men (2004) #60
results.description: Part 2 of X-TERMINATION! With Nightcrawler wreaking havoc on the very fabric of reality, Wolverine calls in his street team. Confronted with the doppelganger of their dead friend, will the team be able to do what’s necessary to stop him?

results.title: Astonishing X-Men (2004) #61
results.description: X-TERMINATION Part 5 AOA and our Earth are on the verge of destruction! Plus, a final goodbye between Wolverine and AOA Jean Grey!

results.title: Astonishing X-Men (2004) #62
results.description: Iceman is changed after his multi-dimensional ordeal. What aftershocks will this have in his life?  And what is left of the Astonishing X-Men, The X-Treme X-Men and the Age of Apocalypse?

results.title: Astonishing X-Men (2004) #63
results.description: Over the course of his life, Bobby Drake, a.k.a. Iceman, has taken on and beaten the worst enemies the world -- and the universe -- can throw at him. But is the most dangerous villain yet to come? And could it be none other than...Bobby himself?

results.title: Astonishing X-Men (2004) #64
results.description: A catastrophic storm has buried much of the northern hemisphere under the deadly weight of snow, creating a kingdom where only one man rules: Bobby Drake.

results.title: Astonishing X-Men (2004) #65
results.description: As the world shivers beneath a heavy blanket of snow, it's time for the final showdown. When all is said and done, who is Bobby Drake? What kind of man will he be? And how can he reconcile the things that he's done?

results.title: Astonishing X-Men (2004) #66
results.description: In the aftermath of Iceman's assault on the world, the X-Men need some time to reflect and take stock of their relationships. What will come from this? And will it send one character down a new path away from the X-Men?

results.title: Astonishing X-Men (2004) #67
results.description: Wolverine and Gambit, on the road, in a stolen Lamborghini…with an alien stuffed in the teeny tiny trunk, and more aliens tailing them. What could possibly go wrong?

results.title: Astonishing X-Men (2004) #68
results.description: Through thick and thin, from marriage to apocalypse, the X-Men have always stood together as a family. Is there anything in this world that could break them up?
